   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="uoedh_hl_h.846_1.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <address rend="letterhead">
                  <addrLine>KINGSTON LACY,</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>WIMBORNE.</addrLine>
               </address>
               <dateline>
                  <date when="1917-08-25"><hi rend="underline">August 25/17</hi>.</date>
               </dateline>
               <salute>Dear <persName ref="#ps:TH"><abbr>M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi></abbr>
                     Hardy</persName>.</salute>
            </opener>

            <p>I hope you will forgive me for writing to you, but I wonder if you would be so kind
               as to send me your autograph with a few words as well.</p>

            <p>I am making a collection of the signatures <pb n="2" facs="uoedh_hl_h.846_2.jpg"/> of
               famous men, and without yours it would never be complete.</p>

            <p>We are so proud of you as belonging to our county, and my Mother is one of the
               greatest admirers of your writings.</p>

            <p>We should be so pleased <pb n="3" facs="uoedh_hl_h.846_3.jpg"/> if you could come
               over and see us here, although, of course, it is very difficult at present to get
               about.</p>

            <p>Hoping you will not mind my writing to you â€“</p>

            <closer>
               <salute>I remain</salute>
               <salute>Yours sincerely</salute>
               <signed>Daphne Bankes.</signed>
            </closer>
            <pb n="4" facs="uoedh_hl_h.846_4.jpg"/>

         </div>
      </body>
